own parse pipeline accordingly.|\n\n## Possibly related PRs\n\n- laurent22/joplin#14556: Adds a Turndown rule and changes HtmlToMd parsing/options addressing similar Google Docs conversion issues.\n\n## Suggested labels\n\n`editor`, `markdown-editor`\n\n## Suggested reviewers\n\n- personalizedrefrigerator\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- walkthrough_end -->\n\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_override_start -->\n> [!IMPORTANT]\n> ## Pre-merge checks failed\n> \n> Please resolve all errors before merging. Addressing warnings is optional.\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_override_end -->\n\n### ❌ Failed checks (2 inconclusive)\n\n|               Check name              | Status         | Explanation                                                                                                                                                                                                 | Resolution                                                                                                                                                          |\n| :-----------------------------------: | :------------- | :---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | :------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n|          Linked Issues check          | ❓ Inconclusive | The PR addresses the primary objective from `#14396` (preventing stray ** markers), but reviewer feedback indicates the linked issue also mentions <br/> and paragraph break problems that appear unresolved. | Verify that the solution also handles Google Docs <br class=\"kix-line-break\"> elements and paragraph spacing, as mentioned in `#14396` and requested by the reviewer. |\n| Pr Description Must Follow Guideline